Jacques Grétillat https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jacques_Gr%C3%A9tillat 0 Jacques Marie Gaëtan Grétillat (26 August 1885 – 19 December 1950) was a French actor and film director. Grétillat was born in Vitry-sur-Seine (Val-de-Marne), and died in Paris. Jacques_Marie_Gaëtan_Grétillat ( 26_August_1885 – 19_December_1950 ) was a_French_actor_and_film_director .
